	dprr:hasNoteText "Legatus in Asia, early first century, but the date is uncertain; known from an inscription in honor of his daughter, Coelia Polla (L Magn. 148). See Syme, JRS 53, 1963, 55, note 4-RP 2.554-558.\n" .
